<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Stauff zu Ehrenfels</head><p>Der Rat bedauert, dass König Ruprecht dem Adressaten 199 Gulden schuldet, und teilt mit, dafür nicht haftbar zu sein.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_93" id="45r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_93_r2l16"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Stauffer /</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l17">von Tumſtauffe</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_93_r2l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Stauffer / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchulde wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l19">als euch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römiſch künıg ſchuldig ſeẏ / <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> als </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l20">hundert vnd neunvndneuncʒig <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> / dauon Jr euch etvvaʒ beklagt / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l21">iſt vns niht lieb / Auch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough">der </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1574683245400_718">ſölcher </ab></add> ſchulde niht cʒuſchaffen / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l22">ſo <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fleiſʒikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1574683252763_723"><expan>fleiſʒikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab></add> / daʒ Jr vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l23">on notrede laſſen wöllet / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l24"> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">VVolt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1574683308267_738">Mocht </ab></add> Jr aber des niht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1574683324342_745">ge </ab></add> tun / des vvir euch doch niht ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l25">trawen / So vvöllen vvir euch darümb gern eins <expan>freuntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l26">ſein / an den Steten / do wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>bıllıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun ſüllen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıȷ̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r2l27">poſt Oſwaldi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_93" id="45r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Stauffer von Tumstauffe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Stauffer, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                                  <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan> schulde wegen, als
                                                euch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch künig,
                                                schuldig sey <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                hundert und neunundneunczig
                                                  <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>, davon ir euch
                                                etwaz beklagt, das ist uns niht lieb. Auch so
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                                  <add>sölcher</add> schulde niht czuschaffen.
                                                  <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> so
                                                  <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<add><expan>fleiszikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add>,
                                                daz ir uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                                                darümb on notrede lassen wöllet. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <add>Mocht</add>
                                                ir aber des niht <add>ge</add>tun, des wir euch doch
                                                niht getrawen, so wöllen wir euch darümb gern eins
                                                  <expan>freuntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> sein an den steten,
                                                do wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das
                                                  <expan>billich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun süllen.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii post Oswaldi.</ab>
</div>
